Subject: [Comerica] Azure SSO Login Loop After 5.9.4.1
Description:
After upgrading to 5.9.4.1, Comerica's QA environment gets stuck attempting to login to Azure SSO. Eventually, we receive a HTTP 502 error. At the moment, we are resorting to using the failover login user.

Nginx error log:

2024/12/13 13:18:51 [alert] 23718#23718: *363094 open socket #7 left in connection 226
2024/12/13 13:18:51 [alert] 23718#23718: aborting
Solution_Comment__c: Issue corrected within new server version (5.9.4.1)
